This paper is about training quantized neural networks, which is a topic that spans multiple sub-fields of computer science. However, given that the paper focuses on deep learning models and optimization techniques, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper applies its method to image classification tasks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Other possible sub-categories include cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these fields are all relevant to the topic of neural network quantization.
